dentified as being of the calcium type and people's chemical analysis confirms that they would benefit from a PHOSPHORUS raising approach instead Ron Roth Internet Rosenet ron roth rosehamilton A stone on the ground is better than a stone in the RoseReader Entered at ROSEHAMILTON RoseMail Usenet Rose Media Hamilton